# ─── Secrets / local backend config (NEVER commit) ───────────
env.js
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*service-account*.json
service-account*.json

# ─── Source APK (3rd-party, do not redistribute) ─────────────
app.apk
*.apk

# ─── Bundled product photos already served from Supabase Storage ─
# Product photos (~96MB) live in the `product-images` bucket / CDN.
assets/products/
# NOTE: assets/categories/ IS committed — the `categories` table still
# references local assets/categories/*.jpg paths (only ~1.2MB), so these
# small section thumbnails must ship with the site to render on Vercel.

